flowchart TD
    CLI[aider console script] --> Main[aider.main]
    Main --> Args[CLI config env parser]
    Main --> IO[InputOutput]
    Main --> Repo[GitRepo]
    Main --> Model[Model and ModelSettings]
    Main --> Coder[Coder.create]

    Coder --> Loop[Coder.run]
    Loop --> Preproc[preproc_user_input]
    Preproc --> Commands[Commands slash and bang dispatcher]
    Preproc --> Mentions[file and URL detection]
    Commands --> Switch[SwitchCoder mode change]
    Switch --> Coder

    Loop --> SendMessage[Coder.send_message]
    SendMessage --> Chunks[ChatChunks message assembly]
    Chunks --> RepoMap[RepoMap ranked context]
    SendMessage --> TokenCheck[token and cache checks]
    SendMessage --> Send[Coder.send]
    Send --> LiteLLM[Model.send_completion via LiteLLM]
    LiteLLM --> Response[assistant response or function args]

    Response --> Parser[active coder edit parser]
    Parser --> Apply[apply_updates]
    Apply --> Permission[allowed_to_edit confirmations]
    Permission --> Files[working tree files]
    Apply --> Reflect[malformed edit reflection]
    Reflect --> SendMessage

    Apply --> AutoCommit[auto commit and dirty pre-commit]
    AutoCommit --> Repo
    Apply --> LintTest[lint test shell feedback]
    LintTest --> Commands
    LintTest --> Reflect

    Response --> History[cur_messages done_messages]
    History --> Summary[chat history summarizer]
